The power adapter included with the device in Europe is a :'''DVE''' DSA-12GX-12FEU (12VDC, 1000mA). ====TFTP==== Set your computer to some ip address in 192.168.1.0/24 subnet except 192.168.1.6. :Hold down the RST button, while plugging in the router and wait :for PWR and 5G LEDs to light up and in the console type: 
tftp 192.168.1.6
binary
rexmt 1
timeout 20
put /path/to/your/firmware.bin
